# Robot Manipulation - Cartesian Control Assignment

This project aims to develop a simple Cartesian Control Package for the KUKA youBot.
The project is part of the Robot Manipulation lecture in the Master of Autonomous Systems Course 2012 at Bonn-Rhine-Sieg University of Applied Sciences.

More Information can be found in the WIKI.
